	 Information Sessions 
		 
			 We will be hosting information sessions locally at UCIrvine, in LA and the bay area, virtually, and at other locations throughout the country. Some of the information sessions for 2017-2018 admissions cycle have not been scheduled yet. If you would like to attend one of the already scheduled ones of be alerted when new ones come along, sign up below. Thanks! 
